chafa-syms-rs is a Rust port of portions of Chafa:

  https://hpjansson.org/chafa/
  https://github.com/hpjansson/chafa

The port includes code and generated data derived from Chafa's symbol rendering
core, symbol definition headers, terminal palettes, printer behavior, pixel
pipeline, and bundled smolscale resampler.

